<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="shortage-n">shortage <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ʃɔːtɪdʒ/    美 /'ʃɔːrtɪdʒ/  </p>
<p>[C] &amp; [U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>不足；缺乏；短缺：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>food</strong> / <strong>water</strong> / <strong>housing shortages</strong>
食物/用水/住房短缺</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>To overcome a <strong>shortage of</strong> medical staff, 10 doctors have been employed from overseas.
为解决医务人员不足的问题，从海外聘用了10名医生。</p></div></div>